<item>
            <title>[LU-19668] kernel update [RHEL 9.6 5.14.0-570.72.1.el9_6]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19668</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es) for kernel 5.14.0-570.69.1.el9_6:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: nfsd: handle get_client_locked() failure in nfsd4_setclientid_confirm() (CVE-2025-38724)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: wifi: cfg80211: fix use-after-free in cmp_bss() (CVE-2025-39864)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: mm/memory-failure: fix VM_BUG_ON_PAGE(PagePoisoned(page)) when unpoison memory (CVE-2025-39883)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: kernfs: Fix UAF in polling when open file is released (CVE-2025-39881)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: wifi: mt76: fix linked list corruption (CVE-2025-39918)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: tcp: Clear tcp_sk(sk)-&amp;gt;fastopen_rsk in tcp_disconnect() (CVE-2025-39955)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: tcp: Don&apos;t call reqsk_fastopen_remove() in tcp_conn_request() (CVE-2025-40186)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2025:22392&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2025:22392&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es) for kernel 5.14.0-570.72.1.el9_6:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: iommufd: Fix race during abort for file descriptors (CVE-2025-39966)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2025:22802&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2025:22802&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
